1.2ğŸŒCSS internal style shieet

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
p{
color: red;
text-align: center;
}
body {
background-color: yellow;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>This is web page </h2>
<p>This is CSS Internal Style Sheet. </p>
<p>These paragraph styled with CSS. </p>
</body>
</html>

1.3ğŸŒCSS online Style Sheet

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h2>This is web page </h2>
<p style="color:red;text-align:center;">This is CSS Inline Style Sheet </p>
<p style="color:blue;text-align:center;">These paragraphs are styled with CSS. </p>
</body>
</html>

1.4ğŸŒCSS External Style Sheet

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="file:///android_asset/mystyle.css">
<style>
h2{
color: green;
text-align: center;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>This is web page </h2>
<p>This is CSS Multiple Style Sheet. </p>
<p>These paragraph styled with CSS. </p>
</body>
</html>

1.5ğŸŒCSS Multyple Style Sheet 

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="file:///android_asset/mystyle.css">
<style>
body {background-color: blue;}
</style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: green">
<h2>This is web page </h2>
<p>This is CSS Cascading Order of Style Sheet. </p>
<p>These paragraph styled with CSS. </p>
</body>
</html>

